---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of service for Bizarre Lineage Wiki." canonicalPath="/terms">
  <section class="section"><div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>
    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By accessing and using this website, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>
    <h2>Use of Content</h2>
    <p>All content on this site is provided for informational purposes only. Game data may not always be up-to-date as the game receives updates regularly.</p>
    <h2>Fan-Made Content</h2>
    <p>This is a fan-made site and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to Roblox Corporation or the developers of Bizarre Lineage. All trademarks belong to their respective owners.</p>
    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>We make no warranties regarding the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of the information provided on this site. Use the information at your own risk.</p>
    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <strong>legal@bizarre-lineage.com</strong>.</p>
  </div></section>
</Layout>
<style>
  .page-content { max-width: 680px; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem; }
  p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  p strong, p em { color: #e2e8f0; }
</style>
